    &lt;Title&gt;Faultless treatment&lt;/Title&gt;
    &lt;ScreenName&gt;Martyn H&lt;/ScreenName&gt;
    &lt;CommentText&gt;Following 18 months of successful steroid injections to my spine I elected to undergo spinal fusion surgery at levels L5/S1.  From arrival on day 1 to departure on day 4 I can only describe the treatment that I received as being faultless.  Arriving at the hospital for 0700 I was quickly seen and sorted and walked to the operating theatre around 0930. Some 5 hours later I was waking up and recovering from a major procedure. The nursing and surgical team were brilliant, informative and professional. The surgeon himself ..... exceptional. The outcome, well 10 weeks post op I am for the first time in 20 years totally pain free. &lt;/CommentText&gt;
